nodes.name: Taurine, 2-oxoglutarate:O2 oxidoreductase (sulfite-forming)
nodes.rxn: Taurine + 2-Oxoglutarate + Oxygen <=> Sulfite + Aminoacetaldehyde + Succinate + CO2

nodes.name: sulfoacetaldehyde:NAD+ oxidoreductase
nodes.rxn: Sulfoacetaldehyde + NAD+ + H2O <=> Sulfoacetate + NADH + H+

nodes.name: L-alanine:NAD+ oxidoreductase (deaminating)
nodes.rxn: L-Alanine + NAD+ + H2O <=> Pyruvate + Ammonia + NADH + H+

nodes.name: taurine:ferricytochrome-c oxidoreductase (deaminating)
nodes.rxn: Taurine + H2O + 2 Ferricytochrome c <=> Sulfoacetaldehyde + Ammonia + 2 Ferrocytochrome c + 2 H+

nodes.name: L-glutamate:NAD+ oxidoreductase (deaminating)
nodes.rxn: L-Glutamate + NAD+ + H2O <=> 2-Oxoglutarate + Ammonia + NADH + H+
